Cooked rabbit is a type of food that can be obtained by cooking a raw rabbit on a fire or cooking range, granting 30 experience when successful. Players may burn the rabbit while cooking one, resulting in a burnt rabbit; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at Cooking level 34 on both ranges and fires.

Eating cooked rabbit heals 5 hitpoints. It is used in the quest Regicide to distract the Tyras guard from watching the catapult which is used to kill King Tyras.
